Tiffany Brissette https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiffany_Brissette 0 Tiffany Michelle Brissette (born December 26, 1974) is an American former child actress. She is best known for her role as V.I.C.I. the Robot (aka Vicki Lawson) on the syndicated American sitcom Small Wonder, which aired from 1985 to 1989.
